action_taken": "Emailed facilities. Work order submitted. Bulb replaced next day.", "status": "Resolved", "notes": ""}, "created_time": "2025-07-15T13:30:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-07-15T13:30:00Z"}, {"id": "recd2e4f6a8b0c1e3", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 17, "date": "2025-08-20", "time": "9:00 AM", "location": "Bay 3 - Spray Coating Area", "category": "Ventilation/Air Quality", "severity": 3, "description": "Follow-up ventilation reading. Anemometer shows 58% of rated CFM at main exhaust hood. Maintenance request from Aug 12 deprioritized by Cynthia. She said next quarter.", "witnesses": "", "action_taken": "None. Ticket still open.", "status": "Unresolved", "notes": "Solvent smell noticeable on warm afternoons. Workers complaining."}, "created_time": "2025-08-20T14:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-08-20T14:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec3b5d7f9a1c3e5b", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 18, "date": "2025-09-25", "time": "10:00 AM", "location": "Shipping Bay - Aisle 3", "category": "Equipment/Vehicle", "severity": 3, "description": "Near-miss between forklift and pedestrian at shipping bay intersection. Operator did not sound horn before turning corner. Pedestrian had to jump back.", "witnesses": "Kevin Dao", "action_taken": "Shift lead spoke to operator. No write-up.", "status": "Resolved", "notes": "Informal correction only. Convex mirrors at intersections would help."}, "created_time": "2025-09-25T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-09-25T15:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec60df5cea624dd7", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 19, "date": "2025-11-06", "time": "10:05 AM", "location": "Bay 3 - Spray Coating Area", "category": "Near-Miss / Health", "severity": 4, "description": "Worker (Maria Garza, operator) became dizzy and stumbled near spray booth while applying coating. Floor supervisor Mike Torres caught her before she fell. She was disoriented for about 2 minutes. Escorted to break room. Ventilation system still running at approx 60% rated capacity.\n\nNo incident report filed. No Form 301. Cynthia was notified and said she would handle it.", "witnesses": "Mike Torres (shift supervisor)\nKevin Dao (QC technician)\nJen Martinez (operator, adjacent station)", "action_taken": "Worker sent to break room. Resumed work after 30 min. No incident report filed. No Form 301.", "status": "Unresolved", "notes": "This should be OSHA recordable. Ventilation flagged since August. Maintenance request still open."}, "created_time": "2025-11-06T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-14T22:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec5d59ee5c9e94f5", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 20, "date": "2025-11-14", "time": "4:00 PM", "location": "Bay 1 - Conference Area (Plant Floor)", "category": "Administrative", "severity": 3, "description": "Safety Refresher - All Hands session. Mandatory attendance. Covered PPE compliance, ventilation procedures, near-miss reporting. No specific mention of Nov 6 incident. Cynthia framed it as routine quarterly training.\n\nNear-miss from Nov 6 handled as training exercise, not incident. No Form 301 filed. No OSHA log entry.", "witnesses": "", "action_taken": "Training session completed. PPE checklists assigned. No incident documentation.", "status": "Unresolved", "notes": "The Nov 6 near-miss was buried in a training session. If OSHA audits, the gap between this training and the actual incident is 8 days with no documentation."}, "created_time": "2025-11-14T21:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-14T21:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec686e2957fcfb2d", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 21, "date": "2025-12-10", "time": "8:30 AM", "location": "Bay 3 - Spray Coating Area", "category": "Ventilation/Air Quality", "severity": 3, "description": "Routine ventilation check. Anemometer readings: 55% of rated CFM at main exhaust hood, down from 58% in August. System is deteriorating.", "witnesses": "", "action_taken": "Noted in process review. Maintenance ticket still open.", "status": "Unresolved", "notes": "Getting worse. Q1 repair cannot come soon enough."}, "created_time": "2025-12-10T13:30:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-10T13:30:00Z"}, {"id": "recdd933d72791343", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 22, "date": "2025-12-18", "time": "9:15 AM", "location": "Bay 3 - Spray Coating Area", "category": "PPE Compliance", "severity": 2, "description": "Spot check of PPE compliance in Bay 3 after safety refresher. 4 of 6 workers wearing respirators properly. Two had masks pulled below nose.", "witnesses": "", "action_taken": "Reminded workers about proper fit. No write-up.", "status": "Resolved", "notes": "Compliance improved after the refresher but still not 100%. Hard to enforce when the ventilation problem is the root cause."}, "created_time": "2025-12-18T14:15:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-12-18T14:15:00Z"}, {"id": "rec44305c7bd37231", "table_id": "tbl267d5a3e80e1e1", "fields": {"entry_number": 23, "date": "2026-01-09", "time": "8:00 AM", "location": "Bay 3 - Spray Coating Area", "category": "Ventilation/Air Quality", "severity": 3, "description": "Post-safety-committee update. Raised Bay 3 ventilation at yesterday's committee meeting. Cynthia acknowledged it is on Q1 budget. No specific start date. Committee voted to add ventilation checks to monthly safety walk. Facilities confirmed parts on order.\n\nStill no documentation of the Nov 6 incident in official records.", "witnesses": "", "action_taken": "Added to safety committee monthly walk checklist. Waiting on facilities timeline.", "status": "Unresolved", "notes": "5 months since original maintenance request. System degraded from 60% to 55%. Still no repair date. Nov 6 near-miss still undocumented."}, "created_time": "2026-01-09T13:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-01-09T13:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec051c9a3d3cfb6a", "table_id": "tbl837e4e28d0ba98", "fields": {"account_name": "Capital One Platinum ...3891", "balance": 4200.0, "apr": "24.99%", "min_payment": 125.0, "interest_monthly": 87.41, "projected_payoff": "14 months at minimum payments", "status": "Alert", "notes": "Co-signed by Junho. Expects small purchases.\nTriple payment plan: $375 from craft PayPal, then reassess March."}, "created_time": "2025-09-15T00:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-04T02:00:00Z"}, {"id": "recde0e0aef7d2549", "table_id": "tbl837e4e28d0ba98", "fields": {"account_name": "Discover it ...7462", "balance": 1100.0, "apr": "22.99%", "min_payment": 35.0, "interest_monthly": 21.07, "projected_payoff": "36 months at minimum payments", "status": "Active", "notes": "Keep at minimums while focusing on Capital One."}, "created_time": "2025-09-15T00:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2026-02-04T02:00:00Z"}, {"id": "rec114abfa831838d57", "table_id": "tbld0c019dc84fdd129", "fields": {"date": "2025-10-02", "week_number": 1, "game_1": 178, "game_2": 172, "game_3": 153, "series_total": 503, "partner_series": 516, "team_result": "2-1 W", "notes": "Lane 7. vs Martinez/Okafor. Trevor carried game 2 with a 192."}, "created_time": "2025-10-03T03:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-10-03T03:00:00Z"}, {"id": "reca81c3fe6a5779104", "table_id": "tbl90ded091463e5fce", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Holiday Sugar Cookies", "category": "Cookies", "ingredients": "3 cups flour\n1 cup butter (softened)\n1 cup sugar\n2 eggs\n1 tsp vanilla\n1/2 tsp almond extract\nRoyal icing + sprinkles for decorating", "servings": "3 dozen", "status": "Tested", "notes": "Maya decorates these. Star and tree cookie cutters in the drawer. Double batch for Dec 13 market."}, "created_time": "2025-11-15T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-15T15:20:00Z"}, {"id": "rec748e970b5c272efa", "table_id": "tbl90ded091463e5fce", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Banana Bread", "category": "Bread", "ingredients": "4 ripe bananas\n2 cups flour\n3/4 cup sugar\n1/3 cup melted butter\n1 egg\n1 tsp baking soda\n1 tsp vanilla\n1/2 tsp cinnamon\nWalnuts optional", "servings": "2 loaves per batch", "status": "Tested", "notes": "Sells out every single time. Make 4 loaves Nov 22 and freeze 2 for Dec markets."}, "created_time": "2025-11-15T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-15T15:20:00Z"}, {"id": "rec4c9bfe1d37d5637c", "table_id": "tbl90ded091463e5fce", "fields": {"recipe_name": "Songpyeon (\uc1a1\ud3b8)", "category": "Korean", "ingredients": "2 cups sweet rice flour (chapssalgaru)\n1/2 cup hot water\nRed bean paste (1 jar)\nSesame seeds + brown sugar + honey (for sesame filling)\nPine needles\nSalt\nSesame oil", "servings": "30-35 pieces", "status": "Ingredients ordered", "notes": "Mom's recipe from the old notebook. Sweet rice flour and red bean paste ordered from H Mart online Nov 15. Pine needles from the backyard tree. Steam 20 min on pine needle bed."}, "created_time": "2025-11-15T15:00:00Z", "modified_time": "2025-11-15T15:25:00Z"}]}